Place hamburger patty on grill to desired doneness. Toast King's Hawaiian Sandwich Roll on grill. To assemble burger, spread shichimi aioli on each slice of roll; between bread slices, place hamburger, which has been brushed with teriyaki sauce, then add cheese, tomato slices, lettuce and onion. Serve with pickles and olives. Shichimi Aioli: Mix mayonnaise and shichimi togarashi together in a small bowl.